{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|Jer|50","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","chapter":50,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v10","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":1,"text":"This is the word the Lord spoke about Babylon, the land of the Chaldeans, through the prophet Jeremiah:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":2,"text":"Announce to the nations;","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":3,"text":"For a nation from the north will attack her;","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":4,"text":"In those days and at that time —","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":5,"text":"They will ask about Zion,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":6,"text":"My people were lost sheep;","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":7,"text":"Whoever found them devoured them.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":8,"text":"Escape from Babylon;","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":9,"text":"For I will soon stir up and bring against Babylon","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":10,"text":"The Chaldeans will become plunder;","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":11,"text":"Because you rejoice,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":12,"text":"your mother will be utterly humiliated;","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":13,"text":"Because of the Lord’s wrath,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":14,"text":"Line up in battle formation around Babylon,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":15,"text":"Raise a war cry against her on every side!","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:16","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":16,"text":"Cut off the sower from Babylon","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:17","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":17,"text":"Israel is a stray lamb, chased by lions.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:18","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":18,"text":"Therefore, this is what the Lord of Armies, the God of Israel, says: I am about to punish the king of Babylon and his land just as I punished the king of Assyria.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:19","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":19,"text":"I will return Israel to his grazing land,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:20","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":20,"text":"In those days and at that time —","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:21","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":21,"text":"Attack the land of Merathaim,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:22","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":22,"text":"The sound of war is in the land —","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:23","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":23,"text":"How the hammer of the whole earth","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:24","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":24,"text":"Babylon, I laid a trap for you, and you were caught,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:25","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":25,"text":"The Lord opened his armory","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:26","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":26,"text":"Come against her from the most distant places.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:27","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":27,"text":"Put all her young bulls to the sword;","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:28","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":28,"text":"There is a voice of fugitives and refugees","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:29","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":29,"text":"Summon the archers to Babylon,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:30","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":30,"text":"Therefore, her young men will fall","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:31","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":31,"text":"Look, I am against you, you arrogant one —","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:32","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":32,"text":"The arrogant will stumble and fall","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:33","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":33,"text":"This is what the Lord of Armies says:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:34","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":34,"text":"Their Redeemer is strong;","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:35","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":35,"text":"A sword is over the Chaldeans —","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:36","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":36,"text":"A sword is against the diviners,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:37","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":37,"text":"A sword is against his horses and chariots","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:38","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":38,"text":"A drought will come on her waters,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:39","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":39,"text":"Therefore, desert creatures will live with hyenas,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:40","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":40,"text":"Just as God demolished Sodom and Gomorrah","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:41","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":41,"text":"Look! A people comes from the north.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:42","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":42,"text":"They grasp bow and javelin.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:43","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":43,"text":"The king of Babylon has heard about them;","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:50:44","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jer","bookOrder":23,"chapter":50,"verse":44,"text":"“Look, it will be like a lion coming from the thickets of the Jordan to the watered grazing land. I will chase Babylon away from her land in a flash. I will appoint whoever is chosen for her. For who is like me? Who will issue me a summons? Who is the shepherd who can stand against me?”","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01